297
00:25:57,473 --> 00:25:58,508
Đi nào!

298
00:26:01,685 --> 00:26:02,925
Đi thôi!

299
00:26:08,317 --> 00:26:10,524
Caesar! Caesar!

300
00:26:11,737 --> 00:26:12,977
Coi nào!

301
00:26:13,489 --> 00:26:15,650
